OL,11,     GHenry Cole and Simon O'Brien
OL,12,     Gvisit Janet's Suffolk garden shed
OL,13,     Gfilled with rare furniture.
OL,14,G1025FA Place in the Sun
OL,15,     GAndi and Neil dream of retiring
OL,16,     Gto Spain with their son Joel and
OL,17,     Gspaniel Dixie. Can Laura Hamilton
OL,18,     Gfind their perfect place close to
OL,19,     Gthe coastal town of Mazarron,
OL,20,     Gnear Murcia, for #145,000?
